<emphasis id="2CC2EC50FFA5FFDDD25520F3FD5E24E0" box="[609,707,1976,1998]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="578">Miroculis</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="2CC2EC50FFA5FFDDD2E520F2FC8A24E0" box="[721,791,1977,1998]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="578">xavieri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="37F1512BFFA5FFDDD32920F2FCF024E0" box="[797,877,1977,1998]" pageId="5" pageNumber="578" rank="species">
<emphasis id="2CC2EC50FFA5FFDDD32920F2FCF024E0" bold="true" box="[797,877,1977,1998]" pageId="5" pageNumber="578">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
: 11) lateral view, habituS; 12) forewing; 13) hind wing; 14) genitalia; 15) apex of peniS, detail.
</paragraph>
